data.description: This is a 4 sided brick ranch in a great location! 3 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath, with a ton of renovations! All new interior paint, kitchen countertops are brand new and the cabinets have just recently been stained! The appliances are less than 6 years old! Really pretty new lvp flooring in the kitchen and bathrooms.. the master bath has been completely remodeled in the past 3 years, with a tile shower and new vanity. Most of the windows have been replaced. HVAC is only 8 years old! This house also has a GENERATOR that runs on natural gas that is less than 2 years old! Septic has recently been serviced and plumbing replaced; several electrical improvements have been made. This location is convenient to restaurants, hospital, schools and shopping! Quiet one street neighborhood.. Affordable and move-in ready!
